      <title>到2029年，芬兰将国防支出目标提高到GDP的3％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/finland-to-raise-defense-spending-target-to-3-of-gdp-by-2029</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰总理佩特里·奥尔波（Petteri Orpo）说，到2029年，芬兰政府计划将该国的国防支出提高到其经济产出的3％，以应对更具侵略性的俄罗斯风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/finland-to-raise-defense-spending-target-to-3-of-gdp-by-2029</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 11:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
